text: Cynisca chirioi is a worm lizard species in the family Amphisbaenidae. It is endemic to Guinea. ==References== Category:Cynisca (lizard) Category:Reptiles described in 2014 Category:Taxa named by Jean-François Trape Category:Taxa named by Youssouph Mané Category:Taxa named by Cellou Baldé Category:Endemic fauna of Guinea
title: Cynisca chirioi
